Options:
  --fix                Attempt to auto-fix audit findings
  -h, --help           Show this help text

Checks:
  - Committed .env files with potential secrets
  - Python dependency vulnerabilities (pip-audit)
  - JavaScript dependency vulnerabilities (npm/pnpm audit)

Monorepo support:
  Automatically discovers subprojects and audits each one.

Examples:
  kite audit .
  kite audit --fix .
